  "_meta": {
    "description": "NBA franchise colorways by era, post-1976 merger. For rendering generic era-accurate jerseys (no logos, no wordmarks). Years are season START years (e.g. 1995 = the 1995-96 season). Generated from general knowledge — every entry has a confidence flag. VERIFY all 'low' entries against teamcolorcodes.com and Basketball-Reference season pages before launch; transition years may be off by a season.",
